e changes are done, you must build the docker image and verify that it works locally by making api calls if applicable.\\n- Then only you can mark it as completed and submit the implementation.\\n- Every component must have `workload.yaml` at its root, refer to the github task.\\n\\nDo **not** run `git` yourself. Do **not** create PRs or branches. Submission triggers commit → push → OpenChoreo build → deploy automatically.\\n\"}]},\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"session_id\":\"121c440b-f753-45aa-a34f-20b71a71ccd0\",\"uuid\":\"c2a521a5-0bc5-4b56-bb27-30387abf4e20\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-24T02:07:55.793Z\",\"isSynthetic\":true}\n{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_013Zts8KpgptRXPQ4Xtf6UVK\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"The user wants me to work on a GitHub issue at https://github.com/asdlc-repos/mmm168/issues/1. Let me start by using the ASDLC MCP tools to get the project context and task information, and also look at the GitHub issue.\",\"signature\":\"\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"stop_details\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":415,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":11144,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":415,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":8,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"global\"},\"context_management\":null},\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"session_id\":\"121c440b-f753-45aa-a34f-20b71a71ccd0\",\"uuid\":\"09854dfd-34a2-4832-ab79-5203ed2d7ecf\"}\n{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_013Zts8KpgptRXPQ4Xtf6UVK\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_014VRB92XZzbmBrT3N7hVcYp\",\"name\":\"ToolSearch\",\"input\":{\"query\":\"select:mcp__asdlc__get_project_context,mcp__asdlc__get_component_task,mcp__asdlc__report_progress,mcp__asdlc__submit_implementation\",\"max_r